videos.title: Mesmerising Mass Sheep Herding
videos.description: It’s woolly’s roundup! This incredible footage of hundreds of sheep being herded across New Zealand’s grasslands will blow you away.

videos.title: RAW: Big horned sheep hang out on Guanella Pass
videos.description: We spotted these big horned sheep on one the first days the pass was open for the season.

videos.title: Intensive Rotational Grazing: 50 Sheep and Goats on 4 Acres
videos.description: Rotational Grazing: 50 Sheep and Goats on 4 Acres. In this video, Tim talks to us about rotational grazing a large number of animals on 4 acres. What do we use? How to we make it work? Stay tuned to find out more!

videos.title: Tales From Tech Support - When sheep try to kill a PC
videos.description: Tales From Tech Support - When sheep try to kill a PC or... when good sheep turn baaad.
